    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Short, horizontal members projecting inward at the top of interior walls, attached to the foot of principal rafters in a roof and generally supporting arched roof braces.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
